eqlVolBalConfigRAIDSetFreeSpaceTroubleDe.name: eqlVolBalConfigRAIDSetFreeSpaceTroubleDelay
eqlVolBalConfigRAIDSetFreeSpaceTroubleDe.description: This field indicates the minimum delay after resolving a raid-set being in free space trouble before re-evaluating..

eqlVolBalConfigRAIDSetDeleteDelay.name: eqlVolBalConfigRAIDSetDeleteDelay
eqlVolBalConfigRAIDSetDeleteDelay.description: This field indicates the minimum delay after vacating a raid-set before re-evaluating.

eqlVolBalConfigRAIDSetJoinDelay.name: eqlVolBalConfigRAIDSetJoinDelay
eqlVolBalConfigRAIDSetJoinDelay.description: This field indicates the minimum delay after a raid-set joins a pool before re-evaluating.

eqlVolBalConfigReamSize.description: This field indicates the number of pages in a ream.

eqlVolBalConfigHistoryRowMax.description: This field indicates the maximum number of volume balance history entries.

eqlVolBalConfigRAIDStatsRowMax.description: This field indicates the maximum number of volume balance raid-set stats entries.

eqlVolBalConfigPoolThroughputRateMax.name: eqlVolBalConfigPoolThroughputRateMax
eqlVolBalConfigPoolThroughputRateMax.description: This field indicates the maximum throughput we can impose on a pool during load balancing.

eqlVolBalConfigMinSpreadSize.name: eqlVolBalConfigMinSpreadSize
eqlVolBalConfigMinSpreadSize.description: This field determines how big a volume is, in megabytes, before it is spread among other members.

eqlVolBalConfigPlacementThreshold.name: eqlVolBalConfigPlacementThreshold
eqlVolBalConfigPlacementThreshold.description: Declares the minimum placement score for a volume before it will be considered for performance balancing.

eqlVolBalConfigFlags.name: eqlVolBalConfigFlags
eqlVolBalConfigFlags.description: This field defines the common place holder for group wide config/debug flags. The flags must be of type enable(1) or disable(0). and the default value will always be disable(0).

eqlVolBalConfigArchivalPlacementThreshol.name: eqlVolBalConfigArchivalPlacementThreshold
eqlVolBalConfigArchivalPlacementThreshol.description: Declares the minimum placement score for a volume before it will be considered for performance balancing when a pool has archival storage present.

eqlVolBalConfigFreeSpaceTroubleEnabled.name: eqlVolBalConfigFreeSpaceTroubleEnabled
eqlVolBalConfigFreeSpaceTroubleEnabled.description: This field enables/disables the free space trouble operation within a group.

eqlVolBalConfigPreferAutoRAIDPlacement.name: eqlVolBalConfigPreferAutoRAIDPlacement
eqlVolBalConfigPreferAutoRAIDPlacement.description: This field changes the preference of the balancing from a capacity spread to Auto RAID Placement.

eqlVolBalConfigHotColdPageSwapEnabled.name: eqlVolBalConfigHotColdPageSwapEnabled
eqlVolBalConfigHotColdPageSwapEnabled.description: This field enables/disables the hot/cold page swapping operation within a group.

eqlVolBalConfigArchiveEnabled.name: eqlVolBalConfigArchiveEnabled
eqlVolBalConfigArchiveEnabled.description: This field enables/disables the archiving operation within a group.
